│                                                                                            │
│ This change modifies `getVPCost` to calculate the cost of an interleaved store group as a  │
│ single memory operation using the total width of the interleaved data, rather than summing │
│ the costs of individual smaller stores. This brings the VPlan cost model's behavior in     │
│ line with the legacy model for this specific case.                                         │
│                                                                                            │
│ ### 5. Conclusion                                                                          │
│                                                                                            │
│ The assertion failure is due to a divergence in cost modeling between the legacy and VPlan │
