│ calculation, ensuring it accurately reflects the performance of wide vector stores for     │
│ interleaved data. This will resolve the disagreement, fix the crash, and allow the         │
│ vectorizer to correctly choose the more profitable vectorization factor of 4 for this      │
│ loop.                                                                                      │
